        "#### Primera Etapa:"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "aU7shoQAFzbw"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "Corremos una regresión entre índice de protección contra la expropiación $(avexpr)$ y el instrumento tasa de mortalidad de los colonizadores $(logem4)$"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "FG-0KG-uF5fD"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Defina la vaeriable Endogena:\n",
        "Endogena = df4['logem4']\n",
        "\n",
        "# defina las variables Exogenas (+ una constante)\n",
        "Exogena = df4[['const', 'avexpr']]\n",
        "\n",
        "# Ejecute la regresión\n",
        "reg1 = sm.OLS(endog = Endogena,\n",
        "              exog = Exogena,\n",
        "              missing='drop').fit()"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "0bnG-0KiGGKC"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "#### Segunda Etapa"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "MJm1KFHMHgfD"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "Recuperamos los residuales $\\hat{u}_i$"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "zubBXG8xHirk"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Creamos una nueva variable con residuales\n",
        "df4['resid'] = reg1.resid"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "uguiQwH5HouY"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "Incluímos los residuales anteriores en la regresión original que relaciona: $logpgp95$: logaritmo del pib per cápita en 1995 y $avexpr$: índice de protección contra expropiación\n",
        "\n",
        "$$logpgp95_{i} =\\beta _{0} +\\beta _{1} avexpr_{i} +\\alpha \\hat{u}_{i} +u_{i}$$"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "wtWicrw6Htxg"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Defina variables X y Y:\n",
        "\n",
        "X = df4[['const', 'avexpr', 'resid']]\n",
        "\n",
        "Y = df4['logpgp95']\n",
        "\n",
        "# Ejecutemos regresión\n",
        "reg2 = sm.OLS(endog = Y,\n",
        "              exog = X,\n",
        "              missing='drop').fit()\n",
        "\n",
        "#Imprimimos resultados\n",
        "print(reg2.summary())"
      ],
